{"tid":241563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［陰謀論］有一班人想拖低網民質素","createTime":"2017-05-13T08:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T12:20:18.000Z","uid":9053,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52031c8ee2236acdb0f143b9127773978a908d95","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:53:49.000Z","msg":"呢排發生嘅種種案件，包括車禍、強姦<br />\n<br />\n總有一班人搶住出黎批判，扮理性，然後有班羊群會跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，呢幾年高登言論成為大趨勢，好多網媒，例如一百毛果啲，密密mon住呢到，總之呢度講咩，都會俾人注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，報紙經常以網民、90後、後生仔涵蓋晒一小部分出位言論<br />\n<br />\n換言之，只要有搶眼言論，例如反社會、偏激意見，就會被炒作、被標籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  而呢啲係可以製造出</span>黎"},{"pid":"f7f22935c84fbd9167213c0d206a235c7f3ea65c","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"屌，未打完出左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而呢啲言論就會成為呢班人嘅標籤<br />\n<br />\n最終目的係咩？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扮自己人，扣你地帽子，製造你地萎靡不堪嘅形象</span>"},{"pid":"5de01dc6077f8c159152f9603a03590f593ee996","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛、共狗死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"0b8a94602696d3977ffe9ca3371c7c4788588d9b","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"本身廢老眼中，你地做咩都係「細路仔」、「冇經驗」、「食鹽多過你食米」<br />\n<br />\n依家形象差到咁，無論政治方面，定係純粹自身層面<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅野都更加被定形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地就係牛鬼蛇神</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/13/170441_24a34a09cfe65c6d6eb5b9d6cff6f6b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F13%2F170441_24a34a09cfe65c6d6eb5b9d6cff6f6b6.jpg&h=661780b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4aa4a4664e5aef845bef76059b7dc87555bac61","tid":241563,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:06:07.000Z","msg":"最弊係有人被煽動後出嚟和應。"},{"pid":"d2eed8c30d7c908ce7c60e7a14520759ab050033","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"我唔想我地咩都冇做過，就變成神鬼蛇神<br />\n<br />\n無論係小學雞又好，做緊野又好<br />\n<br />\n請你地唔好以為網上講嘅野就係真心<br />\n<br />\n以為連登講嘅野就係真理"},{"pid":"225f3915a1aac3789435af210f2bf12a17ab7675","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"開撚錯左係吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb23ae3b4b015d441d6ebfa159fee8cb64503106","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:10:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab1c6583143889361f35dc10c1ca906328f33057","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2bc814e4e97e4c57db36f193cc6438c5872ed3a","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a90813f452ee3003d1229a1d7071b4193732f2fc","tid":241563,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,